OL,3,CWhat is the new body that will
OL,4,Cinvestigate Troubles deaths?
OL,6,FThe new Independent Commission for
OL,7,FReconciliation and Information
OL,8,FRecovery (ICRIR), the central plank of
OL,9,Fthe Government's Act to deal with the
OL,10,Flegacy of the Northern Ireland
OL,11,FTroubles, became operational on
OL,12,FWednesday.
OL,14,FThe ICRIR was established by the
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland Troubles (Legacy and
OL,16,FReconciliation Act) 2023, although it
OL,17,Foperates independently of the
OL,18,FGovernment.
