OL,3,CWhat is the new body that will
OL,4,Cinvestigate Troubles deaths?
OL,6,FThe body will take on the remit to
OL,7,Finvestigate hundreds of unresolved
OL,8,Flegacy deaths and cases of serious
OL,9,Fharm which happened before the signing
OL,10,Fof the Good Friday Agreement in 1998.
OL,12,FThe key questions around the new truth
OL,13,Frecovery body.
OL,15,F` What does this mean for
OL,16,Finvestigations into Troubles cases?
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G2/22
