OL,3,CWhat is the new body that will
OL,4,Cinvestigate Troubles deaths?
OL,6,FThe Police Service of Northern Ireland
OL,7,F(or other relevant UK police forces)
OL,8,Fwill no longer have responsibility for
OL,9,Finvestigating unsolved crimes relating
OL,10,Fto the region's troubled past. Those
OL,11,Finvestigations will switch to the new
OL,12,Fcommission.
OL,14,FProsecutions that are ongoing will
OL,15,Fcontinue to conclusion. The Police
OL,16,FOmbudsman will not take on any new
OL,17,Finvestigations relating to Troubles
OL,18,Fincidents.
