OL,3,CWhat is the new body that will
OL,4,Cinvestigate Troubles deaths?
OL,6,FFrom May 1, new civil litigation will
OL,7,Fbe barred and inquests into Troubles
OL,8,Fdeaths which have not concluded oral
OL,9,Fhearings will be stopped.
OL,11,FA number of legacy inquests were
OL,12,Fmoving through the coronial system in
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland and were unable to be
OL,14,Fcompleted before the guillotine date.
OL,15,FSeveral more had been ordered but
OL,16,Fproceedings had not even begun.
OL,18,FThe ICRIR can take over the probes in
OL,19,Fthe unfinished inquests if a request
OL,20,Fis made to it.
