OL,6,F` Why is this all so controversial?
OL,8,FAll of the main political parties in
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland, victims' groups and
OL,10,Forganisations, and the Irish
OL,11,FGovernment are opposed to the new
OL,12,Farrangements.
