OL,3,CWhat is the new body that will
OL,4,Cinvestigate Troubles deaths?
OL,6,FOpponents of the Legacy Act have
OL,7,Fcharacterised it as an attempt to shut
OL,8,Fdown access to truth and justice for
OL,9,FTroubles victims. It has also been
OL,10,Fclaimed that the legislation was
OL,11,Fmotivated by the Government's desire
OL,12,Fto stop prosecutions of military
OL,13,Fveterans who served in Northern
OL,14,FIreland.
OL,16,FThere have been multiple protests
OL,17,Fstaged against the new laws in
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland and London.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G6/22
