OL,3,CWhat is the new body that will
OL,4,Cinvestigate Troubles deaths?
OL,6,FJust this week, Northern Ireland's
OL,7,FFirst Minister Michelle O'Neill said
OL,8,Fthe legislation should be "binned".
OL,9,FShe told the Stormont Assembly: "I
OL,10,Fthink it is the collective will of all
OL,11,Fparties of the chamber that this
OL,12,Flegislation is horrific and it should
OL,13,Fbe repealed immediately."
OL,15,FThe Labour Party previously said it
OL,16,Fwould repeal the Act if it came to
OL,17,Fpower and wants to return to the
OL,18,Flegacy principles set out in the
OL,19,FStormont House Agreement.
OL,21,F` Have there been legal challenges?
