OL,3,CWhat is the new body that will
OL,4,Cinvestigate Troubles deaths?
OL,6,FYes. A number of Troubles victims
OL,7,Flaunched judicial review proceedings
OL,8,Fwhen the Government Bill became law.
OL,9,FThe cases were combined into one
OL,10,Fchallenge which was heard at Belfast
OL,11,FHigh Court.
OL,13,FDelivering his judgment earlier this
OL,14,Fyear, Mr Justice Colton ruled that one
OL,15,Fof the central parts of the Act, the
OL,16,Fprovision for conditional immunity
OL,17,Ffrom prosecution for Troubles
OL,18,Foffences, was unlawful and struck it
OL,19,Fout.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G8/22
