OL,3,CWhat is the new body that will
OL,4,Cinvestigate Troubles deaths?
OL,6,FHowever, he also ruled that the ICRIR
OL,7,Fis able to carry out human rights-
OL,8,Fcompliant investigations and is
OL,9,Findependent.
OL,11,FThe Government is appealing against
OL,12,Fthe finding over conditional immunity.
OL,14,FSeparately, the Irish Government has
OL,15,Flaunched an interstate legal case
OL,16,Fagainst the UK, claiming that the new
OL,17,Flaws breach the European Convention on
OL,18,FHuman Rights (ECHR). That case is
OL,19,Fstill to be heard.
