OL,3,CWhat is the new body that will
OL,4,Cinvestigate Troubles deaths?
OL,6,FWhen the legislation was first
OL,7,Funveiled in 2021, former prime
OL,8,Fminister Boris Johnson said the
OL,9,Fproposals would allow Northern Ireland
OL,10,Fto "draw a line under the Troubles".
OL,12,FThe Government introduced multiple
OL,13,Famendments as the Bill travelled
OL,14,Fthrough Parliament, leading Northern
OL,15,FIreland Secretary Chris Heaton-Harris
OL,16,Fto state that he was confident the
OL,17,Ffinal version was human rights
OL,18,Fcompliant.
