OL,3,CWhat is the new body that will
OL,4,Cinvestigate Troubles deaths?
OL,6,FThe Government pointed out that the
OL,7,Fcurrent system was not providing
OL,8,Fjustice or access to truth to the vast
OL,9,Fmajority of Troubles victims. It has
OL,10,Fstated that the ICRIR will be able to
OL,11,Fprovide more answers to more people
OL,12,Fabout what happened to their loved
OL,13,Fones.
OL,15,F` Who works on the ICRIR?
