OL,3,CWhat is the new body that will
OL,4,Cinvestigate Troubles deaths?
OL,6,FIts chief commissioner is the former
OL,7,FLord Chief Justice of Northern
OL,8,FIreland, Sir Declan Morgan. When he
OL,9,Fwas the region's top judge he
OL,10,Festablished the Legacy Inquest Unit
OL,11,Fwith the intention of hearing all
OL,12,Foutstanding legacy inquests within a
OL,13,Ffive-year timeframe. He has said he is
OL,14,Fconvinced the ICRIR can be a success
OL,15,Fdespite the widespread opposition.
