OL,3,CWhat is the new body that will
OL,4,Cinvestigate Troubles deaths?
OL,6,FPeter Sheridan will be the
OL,7,Fcommissioner for investigations on the
OL,8,FICRIR. A former police officer, Mr
OL,9,FSheridan served with the RUC and, when
OL,10,Fhe retired from policing, was the most
OL,11,Fsenior Catholic officer in the PSNI.
OL,13,FAfter he left the police he became
OL,14,Fhead of the peace-building
OL,15,Forganisation Co-operation Ireland and
OL,16,Fwas instrumental in bringing about the
OL,17,Fhistoric handshake between the the
OL,18,Flate Queen and former IRA commander
OL,19,FMartin McGuinness in 2012.
