OL,3,CWhat is the new body that will
OL,4,Cinvestigate Troubles deaths?
OL,6,FWhen he was appointed to the ICRIR
OL,7,Flast year, Mr Sheridan conceded some
OL,8,Fpeople would be opposed because of his
OL,9,Fpast service in the RUC but insisted
OL,10,Fhis motivation in taking up the role
OL,11,Fis to attempt to spread peace and
OL,12,Freconciliation.
