OL,3,CWhat is the new body that will
OL,4,Cinvestigate Troubles deaths?
OL,6,FThe commission can only investigate a
OL,7,Fcase when it is asked to do so. This
OL,8,Fwill usually be done by the family
OL,9,Fmember of a Troubles victim (although
OL,10,Fin some cases the Attorney General,
OL,11,FSecretary of State or a coroner can
OL,12,Fmake a referral).
OL,14,FThere will be three stages to any
OL,15,Finvestigation ` support, information
OL,16,Frecovery and the delivery of a
OL,17,Ffindings report.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                         G15/22
