OL,3,CWhat is the new body that will
OL,4,Cinvestigate Troubles deaths?
OL,6,FThere are three types of
OL,7,Finvestigation. A focused investigation
OL,8,Fwill aim to promptly deliver a finding
OL,9,Fbased on the balance of probabilities
OL,10,Fin response to a specific request.
OL,12,FA liability investigation will seek to
OL,13,Festablish all the circumstances of a
OL,14,Fdeath and will be capable of leading
OL,15,Fto a referral for prosecution. A
OL,16,Ffindings report would only be
OL,17,Fdelivered where it becomes apparent a
OL,18,Fprosecution cannot be supported.
