OL,3,CWhat is the new body that will
OL,4,Cinvestigate Troubles deaths?
OL,6,FA culpability investigation will
OL,7,Fattempt to establish all the
OL,8,Fcircumstances in a case where it is
OL,9,Fjudged no prosecution may be possible.
OL,10,FThe commission could use its statutory
OL,11,Fpowers to seek answers in existing
OL,12,Frecords, including access to sensitive
OL,13,Fmaterial.
OL,15,F` What powers does the ICRIR have?
OL,17,FThe commission can require public
OL,18,Fauthorities and private individuals to
OL,19,Fhand over relevant information.
