OL,3,CWhat is the new body that will
OL,4,Cinvestigate Troubles deaths?
OL,6,FMr Sheridan can designate officers
OL,7,Fwith police powers where there is an
OL,8,Fidentified requirement.
OL,10,FIn any investigation, the commission
OL,11,Fcan apply a mechanism to test evidence
OL,12,Fcalled Enhanced Inquisitorial
OL,13,FProceedings (EIP), which may take the
OL,14,Fform of public hearings in some cases.
