OL,3,CWhat is the new body that will
OL,4,Cinvestigate Troubles deaths?
OL,6,FIn the first weeks of May, a telephone
OL,7,Fand email service will be open to the
OL,8,Fpublic to express interest in having
OL,9,Ftheir case investigated by the
OL,10,Fcommission by registering their
OL,11,Fdetails.
OL,13,FFrom late May, face-to-face meetings
OL,14,Fbetween a case support worker and
OL,15,Fthose who have registered will begin
OL,16,Fto explore more information about the
OL,17,Fperson's case.
