OL,3,CWhat is the new body that will
OL,4,Cinvestigate Troubles deaths?
OL,6,FPre-investigative work will begin from
OL,7,Fmid to late June and requests for
OL,8,Finvestigation may begin being accepted
OL,9,Fduring July. Operation sites will be
OL,10,Flocated in London and Belfast.
OL,12,F` Is this the end of Troubles
OL,13,Fprosecutions?
OL,15,FThe ICRIR insists that it has the
OL,16,Fpower to refer cases for prosecution.
OL,17,FHowever, the difficulty in obtaining
OL,18,Fevidence that will support a criminal
OL,19,Fprosecution relating to events that
OL,20,Foccurred several decades ago will
OL,21,Fremain.
