OL,3,CWhat is the new body that will
OL,4,Cinvestigate Troubles deaths?
OL,6,FSome of the investigating approaches
OL,7,Fused by the ICRIR are based on the
OL,8,FOperation Kenova model. This was an
OL,9,Finvestigation into Stakeknife, the
OL,10,FBritish Army's top agent inside the
OL,11,FIRA.
OL,13,FAs a result of the Kenova probe, some
OL,14,F32 people were considered for
OL,15,Fprosecution but the Public Prosecution
OL,16,FService in Northern Ireland found
OL,17,Fthere was insufficient evidence to
OL,18,Fpursue any cases.
